      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "### Postgres spot-check\n**Hub:** `http://localhost:8880/` → **Start bot game** calls `POST /data/v1/sessions/hub/start` so `bb_data_collection` writes RCON samples and **log lines** (Docker → Loki → Postgres). Plugin / KZ / engine text that appears in `bb_cs2_server` logs lands in **`biobase_cs2_log_line.line`**.\n\nBelow: **every column and SQL type** for `public.biobase_%` tables, then **`SELECT *` — last 5 rows** per table (wide columns may need horizontal scroll in the panel).",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Workflow",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "bb-postgres" },
      "description": "All columns on public tables whose names start with biobase_.",
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": {}, "overrides": [] },
      "gridPos": { "h": 14, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 6 },
      "id": 2,
      "options": { "cellHeight": "sm", "footer": { "countRows": false, "reducers": [] }, "showHeader": true },
      "pluginVersion": "11.0.0",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "postgres", "uid": "bb-postgres" },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "format": "table",
          "rawQuery": true,
          "rawSql": "SELECT table_name,\n       ordinal_position AS ord,\n       column_name,\n       data_type,\n       udt_name,\n       character_maximum_length,\n       numeric_precision,\n       is_nullable,\n       column_default\nFROM   information_schema.columns\nWHERE  table_schema = 'public'\n  AND  table_name LIKE 'biobase_%'\nORDER BY table_name, ordinal_position",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Column catalog (biobase_% — names + data types)",
      "type": "table"
